Step 1. Current Ratio  
• Use the balance sheet “Total Current Assets” and “Total Current Liabilities”.  
 Total Current Assets = 6,951,011.84  
 Total Current Liabilities = 737,762.05  
 Current Ratio = 6,951,011.84 ÷ 737,762.05 ≈ 9.42  

Step 2. Gross Profit Margin  
• Use the income statement “Gross Profit” and “Total Revenue”.  
 Gross Profit = 1,075,241.17  
 Total Revenue = 5,755,241.17  
 Gross Profit Margin = (1,075,241.17 ÷ 5,755,241.17) × 100 ≈ 18.68%  

Step 3. Debt to Asset Ratio  
• Here we assume total liabilities equals “Total Current Liabilities” (737,762.05) since there are no other liability items provided.  
 Total Assets = 12,385,382.42  
 Debt to Asset Ratio = 737,762.05 ÷ 12,385,382.42 ≈ 0.06  

Step 4. Net Profit Margin  
• Use “Net Profit” and “Total Revenue” from the income statement.  
 Net Profit = -1,352,379.63  
 Total Revenue = 5,755,241.17  
 Net Profit Margin = (-1,352,379.63 ÷ 5,755,241.17) × 100 ≈ -23.49%  

Step 5. Cash to Current Debt Ratio  
• Use the ending “Cash and Cash Equivalents” from the cash flow statement and “Total Current Liabilities”.  
 Ending Cash Balance = -204,229.08  
 Total Current Liabilities = 737,762.05  
 Cash to Current Debt Ratio = -204,229.08 ÷ 737,762.05 ≈ -0.28  

Step 6. Free Cash Flow (FCF)  
• FCF is calculated as Net Cash Flow from Operating Activities minus capital expenditures (i.e. Purchase of Fixed Assets).  
 Net Cash Flow from Operating Activities = -7,724,112.71  
 Capital Expenditure = 480,116.37  
 FCF = -7,724,112.71 - 480,116.37 = -8,204,229.08  

Step 7. Return on Assets (ROA)  
• ROA is calculated as Net Profit divided by Total Assets.  
 Net Profit = -1,352,379.63  
 Total Assets = 12,385,382.42  
 ROA = (-1,352,379.63 ÷ 12,385,382.42) × 100 ≈ -10.92%  

Now, presenting the answer in the required JSON format:

  "solution": {
    "Current Ratio": "9.42",
    "Gross Profit Margin": "18.68%",
    "Debt to Asset Ratio": "0.06",
    "Net Profit Margin": "-23.49%",
    "Cash to Current Debt Ratio": "-0.28",
    "Free Cash Flow (FCF)": "-8204229.08",
    "Return on Assets (ROA)": "-10.92%"
  }
}
